txt.en: All of your efforts in Adagím within Mûr Ghala earn you a hallowed place among the Kintai Elves of Sul Madásh. You are now accepted as kindred among them.
You continue to prove your value, honesty, and measured assistance to the Kintai Elves of Sul Madásh.
Kindred of the Kintai of Sul Madásh
You must earn Kindred standing with the Kintai of Sul Madásh
